---
import TestLayout from "../../layouts/TestLayout.astro";
---

<TestLayout 
  title="16 Personality Test | Discover Your Type"
  description="Take our free 16 personality test to discover your Myers-Briggs type. 48 questions, 5 minutes, instant results."
>
  <a href="#main" class="sr-only focus:not-sr-only focus:absolute focus:left-4 focus:top-4 focus:z-[60] focus:rounded-sm focus:bg-primary focus:px-4 focus:py-2 focus:text-sm focus:font-medium focus:text-on-primary">Skip to content</a>
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="mesh-gradient pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-60 dark:opacity-70" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto flex max-w-[1400px] flex-col items-center px-6 py-32 text-center sm:py-40">
      <span class="mb-6 inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-canvas-soft px-3 py-1 font-mono text-xs text-body dark:bg-white/10 dark:text-mute">
        personality · v0.1
      </span>
      <h1 class="shine-text max-w-3xl text-balance font-semibold tracking-[-2.4px] text-ink text-[40px] leading-[1.05] sm:text-[48px] dark:text-on-primary">
        16 Personality Test
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl font-mono text-base leading-7 text-body dark:text-mute">
        Discover your unique personality type through our scientifically-inspired assessment. Understand your strengths, preferences, and how you relate to the world.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
        <a
          href="/personality-test/question/1"
          class="rounded-pill bg-primary px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-on-primary transition hover:opacity-90 dark:bg-on-primary dark:text-primary"
        >
          Start Test
        </a>
        <a
          href="/personality-types"
          class="rounded-pill border border-hairline bg-canvas px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-ink transition hover:bg-canvas-soft-2 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-transparent dark:text-on-primary dark:hover:bg-white/10"
        >
          View All Types
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
          <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">48</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-body dark:text-mute">Questions</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
          <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">5 min</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-body dark:text-mute">Completion Time</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 dark:border-white/15 dark:bg-primary">
          <div class="text-3xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">16</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-body dark:text-mute">Personality Types</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 max-w-2xl text-left">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-xl font-semibold text-ink dark:text-on-primary">How It Works</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-body dark:text-mute">
          <p>Our personality assessment is based on the widely recognized framework of personality dimensions. You will answer 48 carefully crafted questions that explore your natural preferences across four key areas.</p>
          <p>The test measures where you fall on four spectrums: Introversion versus Extraversion, Sensing versus Intuition, Thinking versus Feeling, and Judging versus Perceiving. Your answers are scored to determine your unique personality type.</p>
          <p>There are no right or wrong answers. Choose the option that feels most natural to you. Your results will include a detailed breakdown of your personality type, strengths, and practical insights for personal growth.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</TestLayout>
